{"tid":841071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳 茂 波 到 粉 嶺 協 助 清 理 塌 樹","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T11:52:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06d8489b035bbe6de1764b2e418e37e6301f9316","tid":841071,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:58:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波到粉嶺視察颱風山竹襲港的善後工作，並協助清理路面上的塌樹。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波與政治助理何翠萍早上到粉嶺馬適路視察風災後的情況，馬路仍有多棵被風吹塌的樹，20多名休班消防及海關人員到場清理塌樹，陳茂波為他們打氣，並戴上了頭盔及手套協助搬走地上的枯枝，又用吹風機清理行人路，並跟經過的市民打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n今日全港各區都有休班紀律部隊人員協助清理塌樹，陳茂波逗留約40分鐘後離去。"},{"pid":"dd59c11e5c31488a0153bffb28f858708cdabcd9","tid":841071,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=321943&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321943%26refer%3D&d=Rk%2FbIM7tdILA6ESJHrBbmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f70b39e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321943%26refer%3D&h=addfd622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=321943&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"1c35fe6d0103a7d2102afb5cb0e1a44c80cd033b","tid":841071,"uid":49066,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"40分鐘，扣完戴/除頭盔及手套既時間，執到幾多條樹枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8194fe282fd48d92d09cf8ebf843ebd1d313ab","tid":841071,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7bd7db768b480c324e84444d54aeef0a3b482d","tid":841071,"uid":81756,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"1c35fe6d0103a7d2102afb5cb0e1a44c80cd033b","tid":841071